    "%matplotlib inline\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "\n",
    "N = 100\n",
    "x = np.linspace(0,2*np.pi,N)\n",
    "f = np.sin(3*x) + 0.25*np.random.random(N)\n",
    "plt.plot(x,f,'-')"
   ]
